  <metadata>
    <name>2026 Lighthouse Half Marathon (Long Beach, CA)</name>
    <desc>Approximate two-lap out-and-back along the Long Beach Shoreline Pedestrian/Bike Path, reconstructed from OpenStreetMap via OSRM foot routing. Start/finish: Shoreline Aquatic Park (Lions Lighthouse). Total distance trimmed to 13.1094 mi. Not the official USATF certified line.</desc>
    <time>2026-05-24T14:00:00Z</time>
